{"tid":2142655,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大醫學院研究：深喉唾液假陰性率約31%","createTime":"2020-08-06T14:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:33:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d3d47d6b27dc6ca9cb6f1e2767f1486106751d","tid":2142655,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:13:29.000Z","msg":"中大醫學院研究團隊發現，利用深喉唾液樣本做病毒測試，假陰性率約為31%，得出的陽性比率亦較其他抽驗方法低。<br />\n<br />\n中大醫學院檢驗了50名新冠病毒患者563個樣本，評估深喉唾液測試的檢測效果，發現與抽驗痰液、鼻咽和咽喉拭子相比，深喉唾液樣本病毒濃度最低，在偵測病毒基因的核酸測試中，陽性比率亦是最低，假陰性率推算大約是31%，如果患者沒有痰，假陰性率或會再高2至3倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400768&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOgcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=d186ed10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400768&h=c811d675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400768</a>"},{"pid":"cc3af418d0058df8f7520a85040dc59a82bd3a12","tid":2142655,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"咁咪可以減三成確診人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d8e21a402d8be488827f53d0a94263d1da8ec8","tid":2142655,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"越多痰越準？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9eb0e14c1f2759a38434e60fcdcc3d45687358","tid":2142655,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"中國大學？"},{"pid":"f31c185b6305358dfaf3b83c9948ff620737eb15","tid":2142655,"uid":328119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc3af418d0058df8f7520a85040dc59a82bd3a12","tid":2142655,